#### 1. The octagon design looks really good, one thing that maybe we can add is some arrows on the lines inside it, to symbolize the data flow part of our project.
#### 2. We should look forward to adapting logos that look, good independent of the theme, I mean some logos look good on light-themed pages but look bad on dark ones and vice versa. We should choose one that looks good on both types of themes.

This look great!
Since ill be working on User Interface Design, maybe ill try playing with this logos colour combination. Maybe that might help us establish a design guide which i might use while designing the webui
ill try making it more attractive, and will share svg format and source file

@programmer290399 yes, I chose the icon thinking of nodes as different API's and the octagon as DFFML linking and wrapping everything together. 

@Devesh-Shirsath I'm not much of a designer so feel free to go about it as you like. If you could also add the arrows in the logo as Sahil mentioned, that'd be great!
